  <p class="banner"><a href="/web/20100518184117/http://ja.doukaku.org/user/591/" target="_top">99yen</a><a href="/web/20100518184117/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#medal" target="_top"><img src="/web/20100518184117im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/star_gold.png" border=0/></a>

	
